 possibility that, within our observable Universe, dark matter\nstarted with a nontrivial initial condition, implying novel signatures for\nfuture surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Jan 2017 01:16:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Sep 2017 19:44:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-14"}
