ency control. The controller\ngains have been optimized with Particle Swarm Optimization technique. The\nproper selection of controller gains and wind power reserve help to achieve the\nenhanced frequency response of the hybrid system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2017 16:10:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-30"}
